  }, "v13"), mdx("p", null, "H\u1ECD c\u0169ng gi\xE1m s\xE1t c\xE1c th\u1EE3 khu\xE2n v\xE1c v\xE0 c\xE1c th\u1EE3 kh\xE1c. M\u1ED9t s\u1ED1 ng\u01B0\u1EDDi L\xEA-vi l\xE0m th\u01B0 k\xFD, s\u0129 quan, v\xE0 gi\u1EEF c\u1EEDa.T\xECm \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c S\xE1ch Gi\xE1o Hu\u1EA5n "), mdx("h6", {
