    "id": "v15"
  }, "v15"), mdx("p", null, "Hinh-kia n\xF3i v\u1EDBi Sa-phan, th\u01B0 k\xFD ho\xE0ng gia r\u1EB1ng, \"T\xF4i \u0111\xE3 t\xECm \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c S\xE1ch Gi\xE1o Hu\u1EA5n trong \u0111\u1EC1n th\u1EDD CH\xDAA!\" R\u1ED3i \xF4ng trao s\xE1ch \u1EA5y cho Sa-phan. "), mdx("h6", {
