    "id": "v18"
  }, "v18"), mdx("p", null, "R\u1ED3i Sa-phan, th\u01B0 k\xFD ho\xE0ng gia th\u01B0a v\u1EDBi vua, \"Th\u1EA7y t\u1EBF l\u1EC5 Hinh-kia c\xF3 trao cho t\xF4i m\u1ED9t quy\u1EC3n s\xE1ch.\" R\u1ED3i Sa-phan \u0111\u1ECDc s\xE1ch \u0111\xF3 cho vua nghe. "), mdx("h6", {
