    "id": "v20"
  }, "v20"), mdx("p", null, "Vua ra l\u1EC7nh cho Hinh-kia, A-hi-cam, con Sa-phan, \u1EA0c-bo , con Mi-ca-gia, Sa-phan, th\u01B0 k\xFD ho\xE0ng gia, v\xE0 A-xai-gia, t\xF4i t\u1EDB vua. L\u1EC7nh vua nh\u01B0 sau: "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v21"
  }, "v21"), mdx("p", null, "\"H\xE3y \u0111i c\u1EA7u h\u1ECFi CH\xDAA v\u1EC1 nh\u1EEFng l\u1EDDi trong s\xE1ch m\u1EDBi t\xECm \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c. H\xE3y h\u1ECFi th\u0103m cho ta v\xE0 to\xE0n th\u1EC3 d\xE2n c\xF2n s\u1ED1ng s\xF3t trong \xCDt-ra-en v\xE0 Giu-\u0111a. CH\xDAA \u0111\xE3 n\u1ED5i gi\u1EADn v\u1EDBi ch\xFAng ta v\xEC t\u1ED5 ti\xEAn ch\xFAng ta kh\xF4ng v\xE2ng theo l\u1EDDi Ng\xE0i, kh\xF4ng l\xE0m theo nh\u1EEFng \u0111i\u1EC1u ghi trong s\xE1ch n\u1EA7y.\" "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v22"
  }, "v22"), mdx("p", null, "V\u1EADy Hinh-kia v\xE0 nh\u1EEFng ng\u01B0\u1EDDi \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c vua sai \u0111\u1EBFn n\xF3i chuy\u1EC7n v\u1EDBi n\u1EEF ti\xEAn tri Hun-\u0111a. B\xE0 l\xE0 v\u1EE3 c\u1EE7a Sa-lum, con Ti\u1EBFc-va, ch\xE1u H\u1EA1c-ha , ng\u01B0\u1EDDi lo c\xE1c y ph\u1EE5c cho vua. Hun-\u0111a c\u01B0 ng\u1EE5 \u1EDF Gi\xEA-ru-sa-lem, thu\u1ED9c khu m\u1EDBi c\u1EE7a th\xE0nh ph\u1ED1. "), mdx("h6", {
